        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Harrisburg </placeName><date when="1830-06-11">11th June 1830</date></p>
<p><persName>Col. Stephen F. Austin</persName>,</p>

<p>Please pay to <persName>Messrs. Perry and Hunter</persName> forty Dollars and charge
the same to Account of the <placeName>Steam Saw Mill</placeName> and oblige yours
Respectfully,</p>

<p><persName>Wm. P Harris</persName></p>
<p>$40.</p>
<p>Accepted.   <persName>S. F. Austin</persName>-</p>


        </div1>
